                <h1 class="navttl"> Text: Edgar Allan Poe, &ldquo;<a href="../info/pp012.htm#text03d">Tamerlane</a>&rdquo;
                  (Text-03d), <a href="../editions/atmp.htm"><i>Al Aaraaf, Tamerlane and Minor Poems</i></a> (1829), <a
                    href="../editions/atmpc.htm#tamerlnc">pp. 43-54</a>
